Median of an array:

Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/find-the-median0527/1

Java Implemenatation:

class Solution {
    public double findMedian(int[] arr) {
        // Code here.
        Arrays.sort(arr);
        int n=arr.length;
        double ans=0;
        int mid=n/2;
        if (n % 2 == 0) {
            return (arr[mid] + arr[mid - 1]) / 2.0;
        } else {
            return arr[mid];
        }
    }
}
